Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 14:24:05 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 3/6] refactor: dedup session bootstrap and route brainstorm
 via shared helper

- Extract startPipelineSession + sendStartMessage, collapsing three
  near-identical bootstrap blocks (/ralplan, /brainstorm, --flag auto-start)
- Route the agent_end brainstorm handling through the unit-tested
  processBrainstormAgentEnd helper instead of a duplicated inline copy,
  giving production and tests a single source of truth
- Drop now-unused imports (shouldSuppressSignals, parseOpenQuestions,
  BRAINSTORM_OPEN_QUESTIONS_READY, createBrainstormState)

index.ts: 1274 -> 1193 lines.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
